1571
01:42:43,841 --> 01:42:49,652
"Somewhat disturbing, sir." "I never expected anything like this!"

1572
01:42:49,652 --> 01:42:55,961
"I confess I scarcely anticipated the contingency myself, sir."

1573
01:42:55,961 --> 01:42:59,951
