1677
01:49:47,481 --> 01:49:52,181
"Do you mean to say that anyone would be mug enough to part with solid cash just to

1678
01:49:52,181 --> 01:49:53,561
shake hands with my uncle?"

1679
01:49:53,561 --> 01:49:58,981
